REM android_chrome_search.duck
REM Opens Chrome via Android home search, then navigates to a Google search.
REM Reliable on stock Android and Samsung One UI.
REM Copy to: /sdcard/lab/ble/blueduck/scripts/

HUMAN_MODE ON
HUMAN_SPEED NORMAL

HOME
DELAY 1200

REM Type app name to search launcher - most launchers open Chrome first result
STRING chrome
DELAY 800
ENTER
DELAY 2000

REM Chrome address bar is focused on open - type search URL directly
STRING google.com/search?q=am+i+being+hacked
ENTER
